<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ШК Бот — Штрих-коды</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='.9em' font-size='90'>📊</text></svg>">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0a;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .bots {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .bot-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      border-radius: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .bot-card:hover {
      background: #222;
      border-color: #444;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .bot-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .bot-icon.tg { background: #2AABEE; }
    .bot-icon.max { background: #FF6B00; }
    .bot-icon.vk { background: #4C75A3; }

    .bot-info {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .bot-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .bot-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
    }

    .arrow {
      margin-left: auto;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 48px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 32px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }

    .feature {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">📊</div>
    <h1>ШК Бот</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Сканируй и генерируй штрих-коды<br>в любом мессенджере</p>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">📷</div>
        <div class="feature-text">Сканирование</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">✏️</div>
        <div class="feature-text">Генерация</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
        <div class="feature-text">OCR текст</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bots">
      <a href="https://t.me/Ozonbratik_bot" class="bot-card" target="_blank">
        <div class="bot-icon tg">✈️</div>
        <div class="bot-info">
          <div class="bot-name">Telegram</div>
          <div class="bot-desc">@Ozonbratik_bot</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://max.ru/id771692758487_bot" class="bot-card" target="_blank">
        <div class="bot-icon max">⚡</div>
        <div class="bot-info">
          <div class="bot-name">MAX</div>
          <div class="bot-desc">Генератор ШК</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://vk.com/club239550562" class="bot-card" target="_blank">
        <div class="bot-icon vk">💬</div>
        <div class="bot-info">
          <div class="bot-name">VK</div>
          <div class="bot-desc">ШК Бот — Штрих-коды</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow">→</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">Бот бесплатен — подписка на канал помогает с улучшениями ❤️</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
